To Neighboring Tanzania Now And 20 People Died And Over A Dozen Were Injured Following A Stampede During A Church Service At A Stadium In Moshi. Hundreds Of Faithful Had Attended The Saturday Night Service Led By Popular Preacher Boniface Mwaposa Of The Arise And Shine Ministry. Mwaposa Poured Oil On The Ground And Worshippers Scrambled To Touch The Oil Hoping To Be Anointed With The Blessed Oil. Mwaposa Who Refers To Himself As The Apostle Has Been Drawing Huge Crowds To His Church With The Promise Of Cure For Diseases And Material Wealth. He Was Arrested Earlier Today In Dar Es Salam As He Attempted To Flee The Country.